TextBody:
Hello Daniel,

This is the new ticket for upgrading StealthAUDIT to the latest version, Netwrix Enterprise Auditor 11.6. StealthAUDIT upgrades require two meetings:

The first is a 45-minute pre-flight meeting to gather screenshots and backups of some configuration files. We will not be making any changes during the pre-flight meeting. The second is a 90-minute upgrade meeting where we perform the actual upgrade.

Please use the following links to schedule the 2 meetings. Please make the upgrade meeting is scheduled after the pre-flight meeting.

Pre-flight (45-minutes):
https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=YyPf42Ka4caN0PuQ.d9txaGRIQELcASgEfQJvxlruR8-Z&MeetingID=iRcj1OIkwI1M8hj8DNJRgjaU3boO3pdhTZSmfKs_DhU-Z

Upgrade (90-minutes):
https://nwxcorp.my.salesforce-sites.com/cts?Id=PuyKRCc5TxZyfzEE9Zmg5W8ivdTrcmmcyY3N4vHELsk-Z&MeetingID=oyuzJCoUnoxeuBvHmbkSha.PXJZlrmWJoz26eoL5LFU-Z

The Thanksgiving Holiday reduces my normal availability. I'm sorry for the inconvenience.

Please let me know if you have any questions or concerns.

Thank you,


Joshua Sexton
Technical Support Engineer Tier 1
____________________ ______
